lish": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014660, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be on you, O the Imam and mercy of Allah and His blessings, I entrust you with Allah and upon you is peace and mercy of Allah and His blessings. We believe in the Messenger, and in whatever you have come with and called to. O Allah! Do not make this my last visitation of Your master. O Allah! Do not deprive me of the reward of his shrine which You have decided for him and make our returning to visit it easy for us, if Allah the High wish.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay rehnuma o peshwa aap par salaam ho aur Khuda ki rehmat o barkaat naazil ho aap ki zaat par. Mai aap ko Khuda ke supurd (hawaale) karta hu aur aap par Khuda ki rehmat o barkat naazil ho. Ay Khuda! Ham ne Rasool’e saadiq (s.a.w.a) par imaan laaya aur jo kuchh woh Teri taraf se le kar aaye us par imaan laaya. Ay Khuda! Hamare liye apne wali ki ziyarat ko aakhri ziyarat qaraar na dena. Ay Khuda! Hamein in ki ziyarat ke sawaab se mehroom na rakh aur jo Tu ne un par farz kiya hai us se mehroom na rakh aur hamaare liye phir se lout-na aur in ki ziyarat karna aasaan kar de.", "Urdu": "اے رہنما پیشوا آپ پر سلام ہو اور رحمت خدا و برکات خدا نازل ہو آپ کی ذات پر ، میں آپ کو خدا کے سپرد کرتا ہوں اور آپ پر رحمت و برکت خدا نازل ہو، اے خدا! ہم نے رسول صادقؐ پر ایمان لایا اور جو کچھ وہ رسول تیری طرف سے لے کر آئے اُس پر ایمان لایا، اے خدا! ہمارے لیے اپنے ولی کی زیارت کو آخری زیارت قرار نہ دینا، اے خدا! ہمیں اس کی زیارت کے ثواب سے محروم نہ رکھ اور جو تو نے اُن پر فرض کیا ہے اُس سے محروم نہ رکھ اور ہمارے لیے پھر سے لوٹنا اور اس کی زیارت کرنا آسان کر دے۔", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA AYYO-HAL IMAAMO WA RAHMA-TULLAA-HE WA BARA-KAATO-HU. ASTAW-DE-O’ KAL-LAAHA WA A’LAI-KAS WA REHMA-TULLAA-HE WA BARKAATO-HU. AA-MANNAA BIR-RASOOLE WA BE-MAA JE-TUM BEHEE WA DA-A’W-TUM ILAIHE. ALLAAHUMMA LAA TAJ-A’L-HO AAKHERAL A’H-DE MIN ZIYAARA-TEE WALIYYE-KA ALLAAHUMMA LAA TAHRIM-NEE SAWAABA MAZAARE-HIL LAZI AW-JABTA LAHU WA YASSIR LA-NAL A’WDA ILAIHE INSHAA-ALLAAHO TA-AA’LAA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ اَيُّهَا الْاِمَامُ وَرَحْمَةُ اللهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهٗ۔ اَسْتَوْدِعُكَ اللهَ وَعَلَيْكَ السَّلَامُ وَرَحْمَةُ اللهِ وَ بَرَكَاتُہٗ۔ اٰمَنَّا بِالرَّسُوْلِ وَبِمَا جِئْتُمْ بِهٖ وَدَعَوْتُمْ اِلَيْهِ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ لَا تَجْعَلْهُ اٰخِرَ الْعَهْدِ مِنْ زِيَارَتِيْ وَلِيَّكَ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ لَا تَحْرِمْنِيْ ثَوَابَ مَزَارِهِ الَّذِيْ اَوْجَبْتَ لَهٗ وَ يَسِّرْ لَنَا الْعَوْدَ اِلَیْہِ اِنْ شَآءَ اللهُ تَعَالٰى‏۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign